{"entity":{"id":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","type":"chapter","slug":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","label":"Mic.7","rawId":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","book":{"id":"recA2CMdJWbqaoTA0","type":"book","slug":"mic","label":"Micah","subtitle":"Minor Prophets","count":105,"description":"7 chapters, 49 people, 25 places"}},"stats":{"verses":20,"people":3,"places":5,"events":1},"nodes":[{"id":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Mic.7","slug":"mic_7","score":20},{"id":"recA2CMdJWbqaoTA0","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Micah","slug":"mic","score":105},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":6},{"id":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Jacob (Israel)","slug":"israel_682","score":1},{"id":"reccdFYIq50NyxNej","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Abraham","slug":"abraham_58","score":1},{"id":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Assyria","slug":"assyria_111","score":1},{"id":"recQIJnCSmWgA0ktQ","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"River","slug":"river_1010","score":1},{"id":"recgdvRbWEPMp5I0z","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Bashan","slug":"bashan_159","score":1},{"id":"recPoImnA7S93jcHx","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Gilead","slug":"gilead_475","score":1},{"id":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Egypt","slug":"egypt_362","score":1},{"id":"recOQgYeMRMqQbIMe","type":"event","group":"event","label":"Prophecies of Micah","slug":"event-220","score":20}],"links":[{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"recA2CMdJWbqaoTA0","label":"part of"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"reccdFYIq50NyxNej","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"recQIJnCSmWgA0ktQ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"recgdvRbWEPMp5I0z","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"recPoImnA7S93jcHx","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recR0q7lx90aC72zR","target":"recOQgYeMRMqQbIMe","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec875d0vtIB6Hgcw","ref":"Mic.7.1","text":"Woe is me! for I am as when they have gathered the summer fruits, as the grapegleanings of the vintage: there is no cluster to eat: my soul desired the firstripe fruit.","year":-710},{"id":"rec2b7MG7OsX4QOjZ","ref":"Mic.7.2","text":"The good man is perished out of the earth: and there is none upright among men: they all lie in wait for blood; they hunt every man his brother with a net.","year":-710},{"id":"recYkEoVxj3EtYhuB","ref":"Mic.7.3","text":"That they may do evil with both hands earnestly, the prince asketh, and the judge asketh for a reward; and the great man, he uttereth his mischievous desire: so they wrap it up.","year":-710},{"id":"recgNFDVVYTWRCuWR","ref":"Mic.7.4","text":"The best of them is as a brier: the most upright is sharper than a thorn hedge: the day of thy watchmen and thy visitation cometh; now shall be their perplexity.","year":-710},{"id":"reckx4RwNRN6YdVd8","ref":"Mic.7.5","text":"Trust ye not in a friend, put ye not confidence in a guide: keep the doors of thy mouth from her that lieth in thy bosom.","year":-710},{"id":"reckvZCiyw6YMVn0v","ref":"Mic.7.6","text":"For the son dishonoureth the father, the daughter riseth up against her mother, the daughter in law against her mother in law; a man’s enemies are the men of his own house.","year":-710},{"id":"rec1mvElG3Ru8mbCZ","ref":"Mic.7.7","text":"Therefore I will look unto the LORD; I will wait for the God of my salvation: my God will hear me.","year":-710},{"id":"recrECGzrRXe0b26Y","ref":"Mic.7.8","text":"Rejoice not against me, O mine enemy: when I fall, I shall arise; when I sit in darkness, the LORD shall be a light unto me.","year":-710}]}
